						<summary>

						<p>The inscription has been almost completely erased. It seems to record somprovision made for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Tirukkarapurattu-Perumānaḍigaḷ by <hi rend="bold">Mādambūdī-Kramavitta</hi> a member of the <hi rend="italic">āḷuṅgaṇam</hi> of the village essembly. The <hi rend="italic">ēri-vāriyam</hi> of the year had this responsibility of maintenance.</p>						

						</summary>
